{"tid":1902922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好驚武漢肺炎會搞死呢場運動","createTime":"2020-02-28T15:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T19:05:48.000Z","uid":159986,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"674394c6080c5cfc1a9f455c44445ac64000b6af","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"呢排武漢肺炎嘅出現令到呢場運動陷入停滯階段，好多人都迷失左，心裹面嗰團火冷卻左唔少，對家係呢個時候係個好機會去殺死呢場運動。我真係好驚呢一場嘅疫症令到呢場運動收皮，令到我哋之前所付出嘅白費，所以懇請香港人保持憤怒，唔好忘記呢一場革命。<br />\n<br />\n憤怒係我哋最大嘅動力，憤怒令到我哋數以萬計嘅香港人凝聚一齊，即使對家嘅分化有幾西利都不足以將我哋分開。當自己開始麻木嘅時候麻煩睇一睇蘋果呢條片，唔好令到自己迷失方向，我哋矛頭好清晰就係港共同黑警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">麻木係極權最好嘅養分，香港人請保持憤怒。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BGe8Dq1l7Io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBGe8Dq1l7Io&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJPkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=cf5490e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BGe8Dq1l7Io</a><br />\n<br />\n利申:條片得四萬幾views，好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1db7018beb7e9183d826db3115fa81a40c1b885","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"282305ebeea3451488d3279b9b8341760a25a0f1","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"a7dab0ddd4bda2303ea8924fb402608499fa7164","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"bcf5d0f67444c98d25bd1780f656fc3f9cf8ccc1","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"b9cdd6b3dcc2b77ab1433a8485307ddd8438421d","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"9097f743b38fb4712f275169bd731b992c85a202","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"086e012022a0467c9e61e00730737417af5aa024","tid":1902922,"uid":92188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:38:08.000Z","msg":"疫情對於林鄭黎講，真係救命草。一，示威無左，可以一雞兩食，又可以向中央獻媚話幫手，又可以向中央補鑊。二，有藉口可以大破慳囊，瘋狂利益輸送俾建制派安撫，又可以派錢賄賂藍絲市民。三，咩野撥款都可以以防疫通過。唔係就係阻住抗疫。打擊異己唔會停。秋後算賬唔會停。政府覺得自己更穩。黑警得到既錢更多，人更強，武器更精良。就算抗疫成功，如果如過往般善忘，往後香港人既歲月，必然更坎坷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100002799757408/posts/2213683012068336/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100002799757408%2Fposts%2F2213683012068336%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJPkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=d7e7adde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100002799757408/posts/2213683012068336/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"fc0d7603b57d37d367014c9dc8d0488fddc66166","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"ed2eded3f0b56c6bffbf88519dee7fbd0af615a6","tid":1902922,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"冇開始過<br />\n除非全民勇...<br />\n都係算啦連登仔同香港人淨係識好嬲同文字批鬥"},{"pid":"b1a258f4661bf3615a7b1eb46b429b55a26f1f64","tid":1902922,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"老戰開花 重現盛世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e59c8752a9742a1c6cf65e29c1acbb41e5eae7d","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"2c35ec053256c7ca16c7bf7cb9913bcbc08961c7","tid":1902922,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"