名 唔係就當分化撚五毛公安警察辦）<br />\n有無訓住覺都要叫光復香港<br />\n有無唔番工唔讀書 24x365出黎上街<br />\n有無搭過黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果以上有任何一樣野你做唔到<br />\n你都唔係我地cc台認可既真黃絲手足<br />\n<br />\n根據推測 連登大約有500個真手足<br />\n如果唔係你就係連登30萬個警察 五毛分化風向狗 pr公司洗地入面其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117c36b31071305e7cb066d7cdd37aeceedc7d7b","tid":1902922,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c56749b252afe9f4a4213c331c2832b1123bdc0","tid":1902922,"uid":216776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed2eded3f0b56c6bffbf88519dee7fbd0af615a6","tid":1902922,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"冇開始過<br />\n除非全民勇...<br />\n都係算啦連登仔同香港人淨係識好嬲同文字批鬥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"我地負責文書，自然有人去衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:40:53.000Z","msg":"搵人負責block人唔該"},{"pid":"0a840e1504f44fa6bc40b7874b26099d5abb1039","tid":1902922,"uid":201110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e589c85cb0d24731f9f650c633987901a189884","tid":1902922,"uid":10612,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:40:11.000Z","msg":"唔好以為你打左句紅色大字<br />\n光復香港時代革命<br />\n8個字就係手足！<br />\n依8個月黎你有無每次落場<br />\n有無比人拉<br />\n有無比人落charge<br />\n(如果有請貼圖同寫名 唔係就當分化撚五毛公安警察辦）<br />\n有無日日落樓做文宣 叫口號<br />\n有無打狗<br />\n有無裝修<br />\n有無捐哂全部身家<br />\n有無比屋手足住<br />\n有無賣埋樓捐物資<br />\n有無派飯卷<br />\n有無坐過48<br />\n有無案底<br />\n(同上如果有請貼圖同寫名 唔係就當分化撚五毛公安警察辦）<br />\n有無訓住覺都要叫光復香港<br />\n有無唔番工唔讀書 24x365出黎上街<br />\n有無搭過黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果以上有任何一樣野你做唔到<br />\n你都唔係我地cc台認可既真黃絲手足<br />\n<br />\n根據推測 連登大約有500個真手足<br />\n如果唔係你就係連登30萬個警察 五毛分化風向狗 pr公司洗地入面其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"玩夠內鬥未。成日都互相批評我哋遲早會因為咁而輸。cctai好多人中意分化唔代表你都需要咁做。<br />\n要光復香港唔可以再係咁分化自己人。<br />\n14年仲未輸夠咩"},{"pid":"09f7df563608f9b6b92b1a0f696cdd100562182b","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"34fb308a47f6981b54b5a22df23365c7676d6740","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"af051c90fe4fbe2647bf2b1813195dfc27de956b","tid":1902922,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"我冇忘記，香港獨立，唯一出路！！"},{"pid":"db165a1977405e5ccd2e3e44dc1f882cd5c1d617","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"9d6ac1368fc040066177a9b4e44e43b58e073b0e","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"f373c80efe379167078adf478bf8444b87ba9eb9","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"a5d8a6365d6b3153f4160ba1462c3b9ce85a2499","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"cc3f74807af62f1a97d2a3c3a71a93fe8502dc59","tid":1902922,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"其實武漢肺炎係connect呢場運動嘅好機會<br />\n<br />\n可以大三罷, 魔法升級 etc<br />\n<br />\n但香港人真係太撚鍾意返工<br />\n<br />\n錯失咗個好機會"},{"pid":"020547bb0e9eeb799162f12a874eadab6826d2af","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"d83ebbd9e17a1231a31e35b8e8750a4ccab0bdbc","tid":1902922,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB